PyPDF2 library
python has a lib ppdff2 which is built as a pdf toolkit.
it allows pdf manipulation in memory
this lib is capable of :

*extracting docs informaton ,such as title ,author etc.

*splitting docs by pages  

*merging documents by pages into a single page 
 and more.

pyttsx3 library
 python has a library that is capable to convert text to speech offlinr
 Text that we are reading from a pdf file suing pypdf2 library is fed 
 as an input to text to speech.
 
 play the audio book 
 extract the text from the pdf file page by page using the PyPDF2 implementation .
 loop through each page ,by reading the text and feeding it to the pyttsx3 speaker 
 eingine.
 it will read out loud the text from pdf page 
 
 
